object.content:
Come join us October 26th (at 11:30AM) for our fall celebration. We'll be enjoying a great chicken dinner with all the trimmings from The Lookout with Apple and Cherry Pie ala mode!!

Just incase you wait for the last minute to get your pumpkins we'll have plenty to give away!! We'll also have a drawing for great prizes like Viking Tickets, gift cards, and pies. So, don't forget your business cards!! We look forward to seeing you all.

Please RSVP to Jim Zondlo @ 763-546-1300
